for operating algorithm Wasdom ESP32:
Download Arduino IDE.
Operating Arduino IDE.
Click on file then choose preferences.
put the package link "https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json" in the esp32,and press OK.
Click on tools, and choose "Arduino Uno"panel, then choose the panel manager.
Will appears screen in the ESP32 dialog box and then press the installation.
Click on tools, and choose Broard"Arduino Uno",then Broards manager.
Click on tools, then"Arduino Uno"panel, and choose Arduino ESP32.
connect ESP32 to USB wire on computer.
Click "Arduino Uno"panel, then Arduino ESP32,and choose WEMOS D1 MINI ESP32.
Then click on tools, choose port COM3,then COM3.
For Operating lighting ESP:
Click on file, and choose examples,then Basics,then choose Blink.
Then  a page appears press an arrow sign in the address bar on the left side of the upload . 
The blue light begins to point quickly or at medium speed.
